# Skill Phase Configuration — Customize for your project
# Format: skill-name:phase-number:phase-label
# Skills not listed here default to phase 3 (implement).
#
# Copy this file to skill-phases.conf and edit to match your project's skills.
# Phases follow a natural workflow: specify → design → domain → implement → quality → ops
#
# Phase 1 (spec): planning and specification
# Phase 2 (design): architecture and system design
# Phase 3 (domain): domain-specific knowledge (DEFAULT)
# Phase 4 (implement): implementation patterns and infrastructure
# Phase 5 (quality): testing, review, and security
# Phase 6 (ops): observability, documentation, deployment

# --- Example entries (uncomment and customize) ---
# spec-driven-dev:1:spec
# agent-design:2:design
# langgraph:2:design
# vision:3:domain
# privacy:3:domain
# docker:4:implement
# web-ui:4:implement
# tdd:5:quality
# ai-code-review:5:quality
# ai-security:5:quality
# observability:6:ops
# documentation:6:ops
